# ==============================================================================
# LOGISECURE AI - GLOBAL CONFIGURATION ENVIRONMENT VARIABLES
# Instructions: Duplicate this file, rename it to '.env', and fill in the fields.
# NEVER upload the actual '.env' file to GitHub! (Ensure it is in .gitignore)
# ==============================================================================

1. AIR TRAFFIC: OpenSky Network API
   • Authentication Type: Basic Auth (Web platform Username and Password).
   • Registration Link: https://opensky-network.org (Click on "Register").
   • Variables in .env:
     OPENSKY_USERNAME=your_created_username
     OPENSKY_PASSWORD=your_created_password

2. MARITIME TRAFFIC: AISstream API / VesselAPI
   • Authentication Type: API Key / Token Bearer.
   • Registration Link: https://aisstream.io (Click on "Get API Key" for free usage).
   • Variables in .env:
     AISSTREAM_API_KEY=your_long_aisstream_token

3. REMOTE ARTIFICIAL INTELLIGENCE: Fireworks AI API (Shared Hackathon Credits)
   • Authentication Type: Bearer Token / API Key.
   • Registration Link: Obtained directly on the Lablab.ai event platform.
   • Variables in .env:
     FIREWORKS_API_KEY=fw_your_hackathon_credit_key

4. WEATHER MONITORING: Open-Meteo API
   • Authentication Type: PUBLIC / FREE.
   • Technical Note: No registration, credit cards or keys required for the development plan.
   • Backend Base URL: https://open-meteo.com

5. LAND ROUTE: Project OSRM (Open Source Routing Machine)
   • Authentication Type: PUBLIC / FREE (OpenStreetMap community service).
   • Technical Note: No access tokens or payment configurations required.
   • Backend Base URL: http://project-osrm.org

6. CRISIS AND NATURAL DISASTER ALERTS: UN GDACS (United Nations)
   • Authentication Type: PUBLIC / FREE (RSS/XML Feed).
   • Technical Note: Completely free for security software integration.
   • Backend Base URL: https://gdacs.org

7. GEOPOLITICAL CONFLICT MONITOR: The GDELT Project (Backed by Google)
   • Authentication Type: PUBLIC / FREE (HTTP JSON/CSV Queries).
   • Technical Note: Open access for automated international media analysis.
   • Backend Base URL: https://gdeltproject.org
========================================================================================
